entry.content:
Pyare bhaiyon namaskar, Main Maneesh, aur ye meri kahani
YMCA ke baad 3 saal JCB job kari
Wahan Bharat Vishi Roy Mukesh, hum sab welders ikkathe huye, kaam bhi kiya aur masti bhi khoob ki
Phir 97 mein main Canada chala gaya
Jaldi apni line ka kaam mila, Quality mein certifications kari, aur settle ho gaya
Saubhagya se parivar aur mitron ka saath prapt hua, aur bahut pyara samay guzra,
Saath milna, hasna, khelna, chalta raha.
Kayi shauk bhi pure kiye,
Tabla sikha, audio recording kari, 2003 mein job se break li, lekin Music profession na ban saka.
Dobara job Telecom aur Consulting mein ki 
 
 
 
Gaye saal college se phir naata juda, bridge course  kiya
Ek baar phir vo adbhut pal  jeene ko mile jo hamne bagair phones or selfies ke dil mein sanjoye huye hain
Wahi classrooms, zang ki mehak, welding karna, auditorium, culmyca, basketball court, arena, canteen
Aur sabse kimti – wo amazing individuals, wo pyare saathi, aap log,  jinke saath koi bhi kaam karna sambhav lagta tha.
Aap sabka mere jivan mein aane ka bahut bahut dhanyawaad
Is group ke karyakartaon ka dhanyawad
God bless you all!
